Copy left is the offering people, a method for work to be modified and distribute the  copy of their work with preserving some rights to own.
In general, copyright law is use to avoid an unauthorized copying and selling.
Copy left an author givess permission to ever person who receives the copy of work to modify or distibute it.
In copy left some rights are reserved to author.
this is very simple way to make program free software is put it in the public domain.
